    "Management": {
      "text": "The duration of treatment is a minimum of three weeks, and should be continued until all lesions have completely healed.\nRecommended:\nAzithromycin\n1g PO qweek\nAlternative:\nDoxycycline\n100mg PO BID\nCiprofloxacin\n750mg PO BID\nErythromycin\nbase 500mg PO QID\nBactrim DS\n(160mg/800mg) PO BID",
